@startuml ParallelSaga-Complete
title Parallel Saga Pattern - Ordering como Front Orchestrator
actor Cliente
participant Ordering
participant Payment
participant Restaurant
participant Delivery
participant EventBus as Bus

== 1. Início ==
Cliente -> Ordering: POST /orders
Ordering -> Ordering: NewOrder(PENDING)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderPlaced(orderId)

== 2. Passo 1 - Pagamento (Autorização) ==
Bus -> Payment: OrderPlaced
Payment -> Payment: autoriza pagamento no gateway
alt OK
Payment -> Bus: PaymentAuthorized(orderId)
else Falha
Payment -> Bus: PaymentFailed(orderId)
end

== 3. Ordering coordena pagamento ==
Bus -> Ordering: PaymentAuthorized
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(PAID)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderPaid(orderId)

Bus -> Ordering: PaymentFailed
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(CANCELLED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderCancelled(orderId)
note right: Saga termina aqui\nNenhuma ação financeira necessária

== 4. Passo 2 - Restaurante ==
Bus -> Restaurant: OrderPaid
Restaurant -> Restaurant: cria RestaurantOrder(QUEUED)
alt Aceita
Restaurant -> Bus: RestaurantOrderAccepted(orderId)
else Rejeita
Restaurant -> Bus: RestaurantOrderRejected(orderId)
end

== 5. Ordering coordena restaurante (abordagem otimista) ==
Bus -> Ordering: RestaurantOrderAccepted
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(CONFIRMED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderConfirmed(orderId)
note right: Em paralelo, dispara captura
Ordering -> Bus: CapturePayment(orderId)

Bus -> Payment: CapturePayment
Payment -> Payment: captura no gateway
alt Captura OK
Payment -> Bus: PaymentCaptured(orderId)
note right: Confirmação financeira concluída
else Captura falhou (raro)
Payment -> Bus: PaymentCaptureFailed(orderId)
Bus -> Ordering: PaymentCaptureFailed
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(FAILED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderFailed(orderId)
note right: Compensação: cancela delivery\ne notifica restaurante
end

Bus -> Ordering: RestaurantOrderRejected
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(CANCELLED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderCancelled(orderId)
Ordering -> Bus: VoidPayment(orderId)
note right: Void libera autorização\n(custo zero, sem estorno)
Bus -> Payment: VoidPayment
Payment -> Payment: void no gateway
Payment -> Bus: PaymentVoided(orderId)

== 6. Passo 3 - Delivery ==
Bus -> Delivery: OrderConfirmed
Delivery -> Delivery: cria e atribui Delivery(ASSIGNED)
Delivery -> Bus: DeliveryAssigned(orderId)

== 7. Delivery lifecycle ==
Delivery -> Delivery: ASSIGNED → PICKED_UP → ON_ROUTE
Delivery -> Bus: DeliveryStatusChanged(ON_ROUTE)
Bus -> Ordering: DeliveryStatusChanged(ON_ROUTE)
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(IN_DELIVERY)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderInDelivery(orderId)

Delivery -> Delivery: ON_ROUTE → DELIVERED
Delivery -> Bus: DeliveryDelivered(orderId)

== 8. Ordering finaliza saga ==
Bus -> Ordering: DeliveryDelivered
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(DELIVERED)
note right: Saga concluída com sucesso

== 9. Compensações ==

note over Bus: ERRO: Delivery falha (incidente operacional)
Bus -> Delivery: OrderConfirmed
alt Delivery falha
Delivery -> Bus: DeliveryFailed(orderId)
Bus -> Ordering: DeliveryFailed
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(FAILED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderFailed(orderId)
Ordering -> Bus: RefundPayment(orderId)
Bus -> Payment: RefundPayment
Payment -> Payment: refund total (CAPTURED → REFUNDED)
Payment -> Bus: PaymentRefunded(orderId)
end

note over Bus: ERRO: Cliente recusa entrega
alt Cliente recusa durante IN_DELIVERY
Cliente -> Ordering: POST /orders/{id}/cancel
Ordering -> Ordering: Order(CANCELLED)
Ordering -> Bus: OrderCancelled(orderId)
Ordering -> Bus: CancelDelivery(orderId)
Bus -> Delivery: CancelDelivery
Delivery -> Delivery: FAILED("CUSTOMER_CANCELLED")
Delivery -> Bus: DeliveryStatusChanged(FAILED)
Ordering -> Bus: RefundPayment(orderId)
Bus -> Payment: RefundPayment
Payment -> Payment: refund total (CAPTURED → REFUNDED)
Payment -> Bus: PaymentRefunded(orderId)
end
@enduml
